<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Document</title>
  <link href="/stylesheets/style.css?v=2" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
  <script type="text/javascript" src="/libs/jquery/dist/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <style>
    #header{
      height: 100px;
      line-height: 100px;
      background: orange;
      width: 80%;
      position: absolute;
      z-index: 5;
      top: 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    #content{
      top: 100px;
      overflow: auto;
      position: absolute;
      z-index: 10;
      bottom: 100px;
      width: 80%;
    }
    #footer{
      position: absolute;
      z-index: 200;
      bottom: 0;
      text-align: center;
      background: lightgreen;
      width: 80%;
      padding-top: 15px;
      padding-bottom: 15px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body id="blog-list">
  <header id="header">
    <span>月岛雯的魔法小屋</span>
  </header>

  <section id="content">
    <div class="right">
      <div class="item article-list-menu">
        <div class="info">
          <header>文章类别</header>
          <div class="detail">
            <ul>
              <li><a href="javascript:void(0);">童言无忌(10)</a></li>
              <li><a href="javascript:void(0)">杂文(21)</a></li>
              <li><a href="javascript:void(0)">计算机(3)</a></li>
              <li><a href="javascript:void(0)">javascript(123)</a></li>
              <li><a href="javascript:void(0)">自动化(44)</a></li>
              <li><a href="javascript:void(0)">计算机(3)</a></li>
              <li><a href="javascript:void(0)">javascript(123)</a></li>
              <li><a href="javascript:void(0)">自动化(44)</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="item introduct-box">
        <div class="info">
          <header>关于</header>
          <div class="detail">
            <img src="http://images.china.cn/attachement/jpg/site1000/20140903/c03fd54abb761570fec535.jpg" alt="">
            <ul>
              <li>个人简介</li>
              <li>文章（456）</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <div class="article">

      </div>
      <div class="article-list">
        <header>最新文章</header>
        <ul class="latest-box">
          {{#each blogs}}
          <li>
            <span>{{this.date}}</span>
            <em> » </em>
            <a href="http://web.blog.com/blogs/{{this.id}}">{{this.title}}</a>
          </li>
          {{/each}}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer id="footer">
    <p>技术文档 |功能介绍 |使用说明</p>
    <p>
      <a href="javascript:void(0)">联系方式</a> |
      <a href="javascript:void(0)">张玲(334080707@qq.com)</a>
    </p>
    <p>特别强调，此网站中涉及到的图片均来自互联网，与作者本人无关，特此鸣谢</p>
  </footer>
</body>

</html>